{"scriptures":{"scriptures":[{"chapter":13,"paragraph":85,"verse":1,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013001,"content":"So Abram went up from Egypt, he and his wife and all that he had, and Lot with him, <crossref let=\"a\" cid=\"c01013001.1\"/>into the Negeb.","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":86,"verse":2,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013002,"content":"<crossref let=\"b\" cid=\"c01013002.1\"/>Now Abram was very rich in livestock, in silver, and in gold.","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":86,"verse":3,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013003,"content":"And he journeyed on from the Negeb as far as Bethel to the place where his tent had been at the beginning, between Bethel and Ai,","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":86,"verse":4,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013004,"content":"to <crossref let=\"c\" cid=\"c01013004.1\"/>the place where he had made an altar at the first. And there Abram called upon the name of the <span class=\"divine-name\">Lord</span>.","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":86,"verse":5,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013005,"content":"And Lot, who went with Abram, also had flocks and herds and tents,","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":86,"verse":6,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013006,"content":"so that <crossref let=\"d\" cid=\"c01013006.1\"/>the land could not support both of them dwelling together; for their possessions were so great that they could not dwell together,","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":86,"verse":7,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013007,"content":"<crossref let=\"e\" cid=\"c01013007.1\"/>and there was strife between the herdsmen of Abram's livestock and the herdsmen of Lot's livestock. At that time <crossref let=\"f\" cid=\"c01013007.2\"/>the Canaanites and the Perizzites were dwelling in the land.","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":87,"verse":8,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013008,"content":"Then Abram said to Lot, <crossref let=\"g\" cid=\"c01013008.1\"/>\"Let there be no strife between you and me, and between your herdsmen and my herdsmen, <crossref let=\"h\" cid=\"c01013008.2\"/>for we are kinsmen. <footnote>Hebrew <i>we are men, brothers</i></footnote>","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":87,"verse":9,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013009,"content":"<crossref let=\"i\" cid=\"c01013009.1\"/>Is not the whole land before you? Separate yourself from me. If you take the left hand, then I will go to the right, or if you take the right hand, then I will go to the left. \"","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":87,"verse":10,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013010,"content":"And Lot lifted up his eyes and saw that the <crossref let=\"j\" cid=\"c01013010.1\"/>Jordan Valley was well watered everywhere like <crossref let=\"k\" cid=\"c01013010.2\"/>the garden of the <span class=\"divine-name\">Lord</span>, like the land of Egypt, in the direction of <crossref let=\"l\" cid=\"c01013010.3\"/>Zoar. (This was before the <span class=\"divine-name\">Lord</span> <crossref let=\"m\" cid=\"c01013010.4\"/>destroyed Sodom and Gomorrah. )","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":87,"verse":11,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013011,"content":"So Lot chose for himself all the Jordan Valley, and Lot journeyed east. Thus they separated from each other.","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":87,"verse":12,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013012,"content":"Abram settled in the land of Canaan, while Lot settled among the cities of the valley and moved his tent as far as Sodom.","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":87,"verse":13,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013013,"content":"Now the men of Sodom <crossref let=\"n\" cid=\"c01013013.1\"/>were wicked, great sinners against the <span class=\"divine-name\">Lord</span>.","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":88,"verse":14,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013014,"content":"The <span class=\"divine-name\">Lord</span> said to Abram, after Lot had separated from him, \"Lift up your eyes and look from the place where you are, <crossref let=\"o\" cid=\"c01013014.1\"/>northward and southward and eastward and westward,","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":88,"verse":15,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013015,"content":"for all the land that you see I will give <crossref let=\"p\" cid=\"c01013015.1\"/>to you and <crossref let=\"q\" cid=\"c01013015.2\"/>to your offspring forever.","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":88,"verse":16,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013016,"content":"<crossref let=\"r\" cid=\"c01013016.1\"/>I will make your offspring as the dust of the earth, so that if one can count the dust of the earth, your offspring also can be counted.","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":88,"verse":17,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013017,"content":"Arise, walk through the length and the breadth of the land, for I will give it to you. \"","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"},{"chapter":13,"paragraph":88,"verse":18,"section_id":18,"block":null,"verse_id":1013018,"content":"So Abram moved his tent and came and <crossref let=\"s\" cid=\"c01013018.1\"/>settled by the <crossref let=\"t\" cid=\"c01013018.2\"/>oaks<footnote>Or <i>terebinths</i></footnote> of Mamre, which <crossref let=\"u\" cid=\"c01013018.3\"/>are at Hebron, and there he built an altar to the <span class=\"divine-name\">Lord</span>. <end-chapter/>","book":"Genesis","section_title":"Abram and Lot Separate"}],"x_refs":{"c01013002.1":[{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"24:35","start_ref_id":1024035,"verse_id":1013002,"letter_id":"b"},{"end_ref_id":19112003,"ref_title":"Ps. 112:1-3","start_ref_id":19112001,"verse_id":1013002,"letter_id":"b"},{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"Prov. 10:22","start_ref_id":20010022,"verse_id":1013002,"letter_id":"b"}],"c01013018.1":[{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"14:13","start_ref_id":1014013,"verse_id":1013018,"letter_id":"s"}],"c01013004.1":[{"end_ref_id":1012008,"ref_title":"12:7-8","start_ref_id":1012007,"verse_id":1013004,"letter_id":"c"}],"c01013018.2":[{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"12:6","start_ref_id":1012006,"verse_id":1013018,"letter_id":"t"}],"c01013018.3":[{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"35:27","start_ref_id":1035027,"verse_id":1013018,"letter_id":"u"}],"c01013006.1":[{"end_ref_id":1036007,"ref_title":"36:6-7","start_ref_id":1036006,"verse_id":1013006,"letter_id":"d"}],"c01013010.1":[{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"19:17","start_ref_id":1019017,"verse_id":1013010,"letter_id":"j"},{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"25","start_ref_id":1019025,"verse_id":1013010,"letter_id":"j"},{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"28","start_ref_id":1019028,"verse_id":1013010,"letter_id":"j"},{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"Deut. 34:3","start_ref_id":5034003,"verse_id":1013010,"letter_id":"j"},{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"1 Kgs. 7:46","start_ref_id":11007046,"verse_id":1013010,"letter_id":"j"},{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"Matt. 3:5","start_ref_id":40003005,"verse_id":1013010,"letter_id":"j"}],"c01013007.1":[{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"26:20","start_ref_id":1026020,"verse_id":1013007,"letter_id":"e"}],"c01013010.2":[{"end_ref_id":null,"ref_title":"2:8","start_ref_id":1002008,"ver